parameters:
Maid: This person, they're protecting
me... the blood, the blood won't stop...

Adventurer: Angel, to even kill a
child...!!
Residents: Thank you, you saved us.

Residents: Just when we thought a large-
scale magic circle had been deployed in
the sky, suddenly, a large number of
angels attacked us.

Residents: It seemed like the angels
were searching for someone.
PushGab 4 そういえばボクのことを探していたけれど…

Knight: You shall not pass to the
castle!!

Knight: With the sudden surprise attack,
several knight orders were buried. I
wonder if our forces can hold on like
this...
PushGab 4 これはまずい感じかな……
Knight: Angel, why do you attack people?

Knight: Why do angels, who are
messengers of God, attack people...
PushGab 4 ボクにもわからないよ…

Swordsman: The angels burned the town
and took many lives... I won't forgive
them...!!

Swordsman: If only the Demon Lord-sama
were here, things wouldn't be like
this...
PushGab 5 このタイミングを狙っていたのかもしれないね…

Zerachiel: Claudia and the others are in
the castle. I'm sure everything will be
fine.

Zerachiel: After I help the people in
the town, I will head to the castle.
